        {{ section.settings.page_content | default: '<p><strong>Last updated:</strong> {{ "now" | date: "%B %d, %Y" }}</p><h2>Processing Time</h2><p>We process and dispatch orders within <strong>2-3 business days</strong> from the date of order confirmation. Orders placed on weekends and public holidays will be processed on the next business day.</p><h2>Shipping Options</h2><h3>Standard Shipping</h3><ul><li>Delivery Time: 5-7 business days</li><li>Shipping Cost: ₹99 (Free for orders above ₹999)</li><li>Available: Pan India</li></ul><h3>Express Shipping</h3><ul><li>Delivery Time: 2-3 business days</li><li>Shipping Cost: ₹199</li><li>Available: Major cities only</li></ul><h3>Same Day Delivery (Delhi NCR)</h3><ul><li>Delivery Time: Same day (orders placed before 2 PM)</li><li>Shipping Cost: ₹299</li><li>Available: Delhi, Gurgaon, Noida, Ghaziabad, Faridabad</li></ul><h2>Free Shipping</h2><p>Enjoy free standard shipping on all orders above ₹999. This offer is available across India and applies to standard shipping only.</p><h2>Shipping Areas</h2><p>We currently ship to:</p><ul><li>All major cities in India</li><li>Tier 2 and Tier 3 cities</li><li>Remote areas (subject to courier availability)</li></ul><p><strong>Note:</strong> Some remote locations may have extended delivery times of 8-10 business days.</p><h2>Order Tracking</h2><p>Once your order is shipped, you will receive:</p><ul><li>SMS with tracking number</li><li>Email with tracking link</li><li>Real-time updates on order status</li></ul><p>You can also track your order by visiting our website and entering your order number.</p><h2>Delivery Information</h2><ul><li>Someone must be available to receive the package</li><li>Valid ID proof may be required for verification</li><li>Packages cannot be left unattended</li><li>Delivery attempts are made between 10 AM to 7 PM</li></ul><h2>Failed Delivery Attempts</h2><p>If delivery fails:</p><ul><li>We will make up to 3 delivery attempts</li><li>Customer will be contacted for rescheduling</li><li>After 3 failed attempts, package will be returned to us</li><li>Additional charges may apply for re-delivery</li></ul><h2>International Shipping</h2><p>Currently, we only ship within India. International shipping is not available at this time, but we are working to expand our services globally.</p><h2>Shipping Restrictions</h2><p>We cannot ship to:</p><ul><li>PO Box addresses</li><li>Military addresses (APO/FPO)</li><li>Areas with ongoing security issues</li></ul><h2>Damaged or Lost Packages</h2><p>If your package arrives damaged or gets lost in transit:</p><ul><li>Report the issue within 48 hours of delivery/expected delivery</li><li>Provide photos of damaged packaging/items</li><li>We will investigate and provide replacement or refund</li></ul><h2>Contact Us</h2><p>For shipping-related queries:</p><ul><li>Customer Care: <a href="tel:+919090949292">+91 9090949292</a></li><li>Sales Enquiries: <a href="tel:+919090949393">+91 9090949393</a> | <a href="tel:+919910134560">+91 9910134560</a></li><li>Email: <a href="mailto:ajay252551@gmail.com">ajay252551@gmail.com</a></li></ul>' }}
